        <title>Changes in Soil Organic Carbon and Nitrogen as a Result of Cultivation</title>
        <onlink>http://daac.ornl.gov/metadata/bluangel_harvest/RGED/QC/basic/soils/soil_C_N_after_cultivation.xml</onlink>
